PersistentVolume not to be configured differently on different platforms

- Google File Store was chosen on google cloud as our RWX Volumes
- Simple hostPath storage was used locally
- The wally cluster used local-storage that would provides the PersistentVolume required for the Ceph Filesystem and a custom storage-class for volumes offered by Ceph. We followed instructions at [rook-getting-started](https://rook.io/docs/rook/latest/Getting-Started/quickstart/#create-a-ceph-cluster)
